Based on metric, trace, and log analysis: traces for ts-travel-service showed the earliest and strongest duration/p95 spikes starting at 2024-01-23 04:03:00 UTC, while metrics did not show sustained CPU/memory/disk/socket faults and logs had no error spikes. The elevated trace latencies in ts-travel-service preceded increased latencies toward ts-order-service, consistent with a service-level/network latency originating at ts-travel-service.

